Class Mazub

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Imovement
    public class Mazub
extends Jumper
    A class of mazubs as a special kind of jumpers. Appart from being able to jump, they are also able to duck, which allows them to crawl through small spaces. Mazubs like to eat plants, but only alive plants.
